data.description: With $300k in renovations- you will be blown away by the gorgeous new pool, fully custom kitchen, & more. This home truly has it all with 6 bedrooms, over 3200sqft, owned solar, RV parking, formal dining/living room, & oversized primary suite. Walking up to this corner lot home, you'll notice the cute curb appeal & cozy porch. Entering the home, you're greeted by vaulted ceilings in the formal living & dining room combo along with new flooring. The real show stopper is the beautiful chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, Wolf range, oversized island, custom hood, & farmhouse sink. From the kitchen, you overlook the family room with fireplace, and the stunning backyard. One full bedroom & full bathroom downstairs, plus the cutest laundry room you've ever seen complete with dog wash station! Upstairs, you'll find the luxurious primary retreat with fireplace, sitting area, updated bathroom, & large closet. The addtl nicely sized 4 bedrooms plus full bathroom finish off the 2nd story. Heading in to the backyard, you'll find a perfectly curated space with custom pool + spa, pergola, & fresh landscape. Come relax or entertain year round! Bonus: large side yard w/ gate for RV storage & fully owned solar.
